  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/59",
  "title": "Plurals in stats widget",
  "body": "Mustache templating is logicless, which means we cannot display handle plurals in the template (\"1 result\" vs \"42 results\").\n\nA way to do it would be to pass a `isPlural` key to the data passed to the template but this won't cover all cases (some languages have different plurals for 1+, 2+, 3+).\n",
